senschaftlicher Mitarbeiter des Militärgeschichtlichen Forschungsamtes Potsdam.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aHistoryxHistorical PeriodsxContemporary HistoryxContemporary History since 1945. 4aSiebzehnter Juni. 70(DE-588)4181209-80(DE-627)1053199530(DE-576)210003324aSiebzehnter Juni2gnd 7aHISTORY / General.2bisacsh1 aDiedrich, Torsten, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA History 2000 - 2014z9783110635836oZDB-23-GHI0 cprintz978348656735940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978348683412340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486834123423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486834123/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GHIc2000d2014